data.description: Don't miss this well maintained 3-bedroom 2 bath home located in quiet neighborhood, with no HOA in rural Newton County! Home features a large living room/Family room with fireplace and opens to the eat in kitchen complete with a large island, white cabinets with solid surface counter tops, and stainless-steel appliances. Down the hallway you will find the laundry area and a full bathroom. The Secondary bedrooms are nicely sized. The large master bedroom complete with ensuite bath is roomy enough for a king-sized bed! The backyard is fenced and is perfect for those summer BBQ'S!
